00:01:59.121 --> 00:02:01.401
I love the noodles
Quecha makes. So tasty.

00:02:01.401 --> 00:02:02.160
Right.

00:02:02.520 --> 00:02:03.360
Slow down.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:04.240
Some toppings.

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:05.761
Eat with us.

00:02:05.761 --> 00:02:06.561
Fantastic.

00:02:06.641 --> 00:02:07.520
Come on.

00:02:08.320 --> 00:02:09.121
Smells amazing.

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:10.081
Can we finish it all?

00:02:10.081 --> 00:02:10.961
My turn now?

00:02:11.480 --> 00:02:12.361
Hold on.

00:02:13.121 --> 00:02:14.841
Your snoring kept everyone awake.

00:02:14.920 --> 00:02:16.561
When do I snore?

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:19.480
Not just snoring,
you grind your teeth too.

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:21.600
Why not mention his farting?

00:02:21.600 --> 00:02:23.401
Who? You're the farter.

00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:24.521
It's from Jiang's phone.

00:02:24.521 --> 00:02:25.200
Give me some too.

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:25.880
Here.

00:02:26.440 --> 00:02:27.281
(Jiang Baichuan)
Who wants more toppings?

00:02:27.561 --> 00:02:28.561
No more for me.

00:02:29.241 --> 00:02:30.241
Just got more.

00:02:31.521 --> 00:02:32.281
Delicious.

00:02:43.160 --> 00:02:45.521
How are my people?

00:02:45.880 --> 00:02:47.001
Earth Fiends are tough.

00:02:48.121 --> 00:02:49.600
They won't die easily.

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:52.841
But under my watch,

00:02:53.561 --> 00:02:55.160
we've got many hot-headed hunters.

00:02:55.480 --> 00:02:57.640
They might lose control
if this drags on.

00:03:01.320 --> 00:03:05.600
True, Earth Fiends are resilient.

00:03:06.801 --> 00:03:09.600
But Jiang Baichuan isn't an Earth Fiend.

00:03:11.241 --> 00:03:12.640
Those four Earth Fiends

00:03:13.440 --> 00:03:15.040
must be important to you.

00:03:15.600 --> 00:03:17.640
Why else did you hide them so securely?

00:03:17.841 --> 00:03:19.521
Since we both have bargaining chips,

00:03:20.880 --> 00:03:22.081
let's negotiate directly.

00:03:24.121 --> 00:03:25.720
All terms are on the table.

00:03:26.001 --> 00:03:27.281
Nothing left to negotiate.

00:03:27.801 --> 00:03:30.801
Fine. Five for five then.

00:03:32.521 --> 00:03:35.760
Jiang Baichuan and four hunters

00:03:36.281 --> 00:03:38.160
for my four companions

00:03:39.480 --> 00:03:40.521
and Lin Ling.

00:03:41.401 --> 00:03:44.001
I don't know any Lin Ling.

00:03:44.640 --> 00:03:45.640
She's not here.

00:03:46.440 --> 00:03:48.841
But I have not just four fresh ones

00:03:50.001 --> 00:03:52.121
but also an old friend of yours.

00:03:52.600 --> 00:03:53.241
Who?

00:03:53.841 --> 00:03:54.521
Chen Fu.

00:04:02.801 --> 00:04:06.081
(Quecha)
How about adding one more each?

00:04:09.361 --> 00:04:10.401
Meaning?

00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:13.081
Besides Jiang Baichuan
and four other hunters,

00:04:14.320 --> 00:04:15.720
I want one more person.

00:04:16.760 --> 00:04:17.241
Who is it?

00:04:19.840 --> 00:04:20.561
Yan Tuo.

00:05:20.650 --> 00:05:22.131
You won't eat thrown-down food.

00:05:22.371 --> 00:05:25.050
You'll take it
if I deliver it personally, right?

00:05:36.234 --> 00:05:37.073
Got a mirror?

00:05:41.874 --> 00:05:42.513
Why?

00:05:45.794 --> 00:05:46.874
Just want to see

00:05:47.994 --> 00:05:49.474
if I still look human.

00:05:55.466 --> 00:05:56.106
Thanks.

00:05:56.714 --> 00:05:58.515
You're throwing away a good life.

00:06:00.594 --> 00:06:01.274
Is it worth it?

00:06:03.594 --> 00:06:06.435
I thought of all people...

00:06:07.395 --> 00:06:08.994
you'd be the one to believe me.

00:06:12.474 --> 00:06:13.794
How can I believe you?

00:06:35.635 --> 00:06:37.594
Xiong, Feng insisted...

00:06:45.195 --> 00:06:45.794
Xiong Hei.

00:07:00.234 --> 00:07:02.354
Four of my closest companions

00:07:02.474 --> 00:07:03.994
disappeared together.

00:07:05.075 --> 00:07:06.794
Do you know what happened?

00:07:08.394 --> 00:07:10.075
I've been locked up here.

00:07:10.435 --> 00:07:12.354
How would I know about outside affairs?

00:07:13.594 --> 00:07:14.474
Where's Lin Ling?

00:07:15.195 --> 00:07:16.394
Where is she now?

00:07:19.530 --> 00:07:20.810
Lin Ling is also missing?

00:07:22.971 --> 00:07:26.251
Xiong, what's going on with you?

00:07:26.731 --> 00:07:29.211
How could you be so careless
as to lose five people at once?

00:07:29.491 --> 00:07:31.890
The South Mountain Hunters
proposed a hostage exchange.

00:07:32.650 --> 00:07:34.650
They want to trade
four of our missing members

00:07:34.650 --> 00:07:35.890
for Jiang Baichuan

00:07:36.290 --> 00:07:37.410
and

00:07:38.251 --> 00:07:39.971
another person.

00:07:40.930 --> 00:07:42.170
Guess who?

00:07:45.834 --> 00:07:47.393
If you don't trust me,

00:07:49.514 --> 00:07:51.954
everything that happens
would somehow be my fault.

00:07:52.474 --> 00:07:52.954
What else...

00:07:52.954 --> 00:07:53.594
It's you.

00:08:04.153 --> 00:08:06.033
The extra exchange target is you.

00:08:08.594 --> 00:08:09.594
Me?

00:08:12.106 --> 00:08:13.506
You've always been like this.

00:08:14.346 --> 00:08:18.067
Obedient and compliant on the surface,

00:08:19.187 --> 00:08:23.027
but when you make mistakes,
you'll never admit them.

00:08:24.506 --> 00:08:26.147
Unless I catch you red-handed,

00:08:26.947 --> 00:08:28.787
you'll take the denial to your grave.

00:08:30.538 --> 00:08:31.379
In fifth grade,

00:08:33.219 --> 00:08:35.178
I remember it was summer,

00:08:35.578 --> 00:08:36.739
and I lied to you,

00:08:38.578 --> 00:08:40.899
telling you school
required 50 yuan for materials.

00:08:43.019 --> 00:08:45.979
But secretly, I used that money

00:08:47.139 --> 00:08:48.339
to buy CDs.

00:08:49.098 --> 00:08:50.458
Later, when you did laundry,

00:08:50.539 --> 00:08:52.018
you found 10 yuan left in my pocket.

00:08:53.978 --> 00:08:56.378
You claimed the teacher
praised your grades

00:08:57.338 --> 00:08:58.419
and gave us a discount.

00:08:59.179 --> 00:09:01.019
Then you gave me another 100 yuan,

00:09:03.858 --> 00:09:06.179
telling me to buy whatever I wanted.

00:09:08.970 --> 00:09:09.730
You said,

00:09:11.129 --> 00:09:12.210
"My child"

00:09:13.809 --> 00:09:16.490
"should never skulk around timidly."

00:09:18.250 --> 00:09:19.570
"If you want something,"

00:09:20.289 --> 00:09:22.730
"claim it openly and boldly."

00:09:24.490 --> 00:09:27.809
"Even if you must seize it,"

00:09:29.049 --> 00:09:30.289
"satisfy your desires."

00:09:37.090 --> 00:09:39.490
I won't give you 100 yuan this time.

00:09:41.409 --> 00:09:43.370
I've given you too many chances,

00:09:44.570 --> 00:09:46.330
all squandered by you.

00:10:06.009 --> 00:10:06.850
I'm sorry.

00:10:09.090 --> 00:10:10.210
I truly

00:10:13.129 --> 00:10:14.730
considered you family all along.

00:10:15.570 --> 00:10:16.690
I genuinely wanted

00:10:18.490 --> 00:10:20.370
to live harmoniously with you.

00:10:31.690 --> 00:10:32.649
What a pity

00:10:36.370 --> 00:10:38.769
that I happened to read that diary.

00:10:42.049 --> 00:10:42.850
It was you

00:10:43.929 --> 00:10:45.409
who killed my parents.

00:10:46.450 --> 00:10:48.570
Did you think stealing Lin Xirou's name

00:10:50.289 --> 00:10:52.009
and inheriting Roadsound Mining

00:10:52.009 --> 00:10:53.330
would make you my mother?

00:10:54.009 --> 00:10:56.250
That you could become a proper human?

00:10:59.450 --> 00:11:00.850
You're no Lin Xirou.

00:11:02.769 --> 00:11:03.450
No.

00:11:05.370 --> 00:11:06.289
You all

00:11:07.649 --> 00:11:10.169
aren't even worthy
of having human names.

00:12:10.330 --> 00:12:12.850
Lin Xirou called using Jiang's phone.

00:12:13.090 --> 00:12:14.370
She proposed a hostage exchange.

00:12:15.370 --> 00:12:16.169
Perfect.

00:12:17.409 --> 00:12:18.929
She's starting to get anxious.

00:12:20.730 --> 00:12:21.690
How did your talk go?

00:12:23.049 --> 00:12:24.850
We just showed each other our cards.

00:12:25.490 --> 00:12:27.370
We haven't gotten to the details yet.

00:12:28.210 --> 00:12:29.289
That's why I

00:12:31.690 --> 00:12:34.490
called you first to discuss it

00:12:35.049 --> 00:12:36.450
to see how we should proceed.

00:12:39.274 --> 00:12:40.115
I've moved Lin Ling

00:12:40.115 --> 00:12:41.514
to a secure location.

00:12:43.274 --> 00:12:44.995
If Lin Xirou bargains,

00:12:45.235 --> 00:12:46.315
use it to string her along.

00:12:46.674 --> 00:12:49.554
No wonder Lin Xirou
also mentioned Lin Ling.

00:12:49.794 --> 00:12:51.955
But I didn't know
you had already rescued her.

00:12:52.195 --> 00:12:53.434
So I didn't respond.

00:12:53.715 --> 00:12:55.955
It's fine. It was an emergency.

00:12:58.674 --> 00:13:00.355
But I mentioned another person.

00:13:02.995 --> 00:13:03.595
Who?

00:13:05.514 --> 00:13:06.195
Yan Tuo.

00:13:11.914 --> 00:13:14.115
W-What are you saying?

00:13:14.875 --> 00:13:17.434
You said Lin Xirou confined him,

00:13:17.875 --> 00:13:19.034
and you wanted to save him.

00:13:19.794 --> 00:13:20.835
So I thought

00:13:21.355 --> 00:13:22.554
we could use him

00:13:22.554 --> 00:13:23.835
as an exchange bargaining chip.

00:13:23.914 --> 00:13:25.554
You told Lin Xirou

00:13:26.514 --> 00:13:28.075
we want Yan Tuo in exchange?

00:13:31.875 --> 00:13:33.715
Lin Xirou was already
suspecting Yan Tuo.

00:13:33.955 --> 00:13:36.075
You confirmed her suspicions
about him as a traitor.

00:13:36.595 --> 00:13:38.634
Creating more chaos for them

00:13:38.858 --> 00:13:40.537
gives us better odds.

00:13:41.817 --> 00:13:42.618
Xing Shen,

00:13:43.754 --> 00:13:45.034
from beginning to end,

00:13:46.713 --> 00:13:48.433
you've only cared about yourself.

00:16:19.434 --> 00:16:21.833
Why are humans afraid of the dark?

00:16:26.194 --> 00:16:28.954
Humans aren't afraid of the dark.

00:16:29.714 --> 00:16:31.313
They're afraid of the unknown.

00:16:32.874 --> 00:16:34.833
When everything is clear and obvious,

00:16:35.634 --> 00:16:37.073
and there's no unknown,

00:16:37.954 --> 00:16:39.313
then we're afraid of nothing.

00:16:39.833 --> 00:16:41.793
If the unknown doesn't even exist,

00:16:42.674 --> 00:16:45.434
then reverence vanishes.

00:16:46.394 --> 00:16:48.474
Humans always make similar mistakes.

00:16:49.313 --> 00:16:52.234
They tend to cross boundaries
that should be respected.

00:16:57.553 --> 00:16:59.073
Since you look down on humans so much,

00:17:01.154 --> 00:17:02.593
why insist on being human then?

00:17:03.914 --> 00:17:05.394
We're also afraid of the dark.

00:17:08.073 --> 00:17:11.954
As long as our kind can live in peace,

00:17:12.634 --> 00:17:15.273
without fear and panic,

00:17:15.914 --> 00:17:17.234
we'll do whatever it takes.

00:17:18.674 --> 00:17:21.234
But this privilege is only granted

00:17:21.833 --> 00:17:22.513
to humans.

00:17:25.753 --> 00:17:28.593
Humans earned these rights
through effort,

00:17:29.234 --> 00:17:32.793
not by consuming human flesh and blood.

00:17:34.474 --> 00:17:35.194
Right.

00:17:36.513 --> 00:17:38.154
Efforts to create wars,

00:17:38.474 --> 00:17:40.194
efforts to spread diseases,

00:17:40.994 --> 00:17:44.154
massacring countless lives
yet being glorified for eternity.

00:17:46.714 --> 00:17:48.033
All I wanted

00:17:48.313 --> 00:17:51.194
was to build a home under the sun.

00:17:51.833 --> 00:17:53.833
Yet I'm labeled as utterly evil.

00:17:54.986 --> 00:17:56.066
I brought you here

00:17:56.667 --> 00:17:59.026
because this is where I originated.

00:17:59.986 --> 00:18:02.107
Humans and fiends,
and fiends and humans.

00:18:02.867 --> 00:18:05.347
No need to distinguish them here.

00:18:09.387 --> 00:18:11.147
This will be your home from now on.

00:18:13.306 --> 00:18:15.546
Since everything's laid bare,

00:18:16.546 --> 00:18:18.147
you have nothing to fear.

00:18:20.706 --> 00:18:21.387
Home?

00:18:22.706 --> 00:18:23.786
I can't remember

00:18:24.466 --> 00:18:27.746
how many years it's been
since I had my own home.

00:18:29.026 --> 00:18:30.667
Do you think I still have a home?

00:18:33.147 --> 00:18:34.667
The only one in this world

00:18:34.667 --> 00:18:36.667
that let me pretend to be human

00:18:37.347 --> 00:18:38.107
was you.

00:18:39.706 --> 00:18:40.627
But Tuo,

00:18:41.587 --> 00:18:42.347
without you,

00:18:42.947 --> 00:18:44.266
I lose my home too.

00:18:45.347 --> 00:18:47.107
You've deceived me many times,

00:18:48.066 --> 00:18:49.387
but none of it was your fault.

00:18:50.546 --> 00:18:52.706
The one helping you deceive me
wasn't Lin Ling,

00:18:52.786 --> 00:18:53.907
Lv Xian,

00:18:54.147 --> 00:18:56.427
or your artist girlfriend.

00:18:58.090 --> 00:19:00.449
Your greatest accomplice all along

00:19:03.489 --> 00:19:04.370
was me.

00:19:07.130 --> 00:19:07.930
I helped you

00:19:07.930 --> 00:19:10.249
deceive myself repeatedly,

00:19:10.650 --> 00:19:12.170
convincing myself.

00:19:19.810 --> 00:19:20.890
But such things

00:19:21.729 --> 00:19:22.890
won't happen again.

00:19:25.370 --> 00:19:26.170
Because 'home'

00:19:26.170 --> 00:19:28.769
is just a fabricated concept of yours.

00:19:30.130 --> 00:19:31.090
Better off without it.

00:19:33.850 --> 00:19:36.610
I have my own kind, my clan.

00:19:37.249 --> 00:19:39.449
They're what truly matter to me.

00:19:49.049 --> 00:19:50.410
From today onward,

00:19:51.330 --> 00:19:53.769
humans stay human,
and fiends stay fiends.

00:19:54.489 --> 00:19:56.810
We'll keep clear boundaries.

00:20:35.850 --> 00:20:37.610
Only this much after purification?

00:20:38.771 --> 00:20:42.451
It resembles a jellyfish
with a jade sheen.

00:20:42.850 --> 00:20:44.090
This must be it.

00:20:45.650 --> 00:20:48.330
Jellyfish.

00:20:49.850 --> 00:20:51.850
Edible jellyfish, delicious.

00:20:53.810 --> 00:20:55.090
We can't eat this.

00:20:57.771 --> 00:20:59.370
Though we could let it try.

00:21:25.251 --> 00:21:25.931
Never mind.

00:21:27.650 --> 00:21:28.451
Yan Tuo?

00:21:28.691 --> 00:21:29.370
Don't save me.

00:21:31.171 --> 00:21:31.931
Let go.

00:23:15.786 --> 00:23:22.097
(Peaceful)

00:23:22.097 --> 00:23:28.232
(Homecoming)

00:23:39.406 --> 00:23:43.244
(Lu,)

00:23:46.250 --> 00:23:48.889
(you've got some
unconventional connections.)

00:23:48.889 --> 00:23:51.850
(Investigate
Roadsound Group's assets for me.)

00:23:51.850 --> 00:23:54.689
(The more detailed, the better.)

00:24:12.409 --> 00:24:14.850
Ms. Lin, what's this about?

00:24:17.969 --> 00:24:19.250
To remind me

00:24:20.449 --> 00:24:24.209
to never develop feelings
for humans again.

00:24:25.570 --> 00:24:28.050
I've deployed all available personnel

00:24:28.050 --> 00:24:30.169
to search for Lin Ling.

00:24:30.449 --> 00:24:31.489
Don't worry, Ms. Lin.

00:24:31.929 --> 00:24:33.889
I'll definitely bring Lin Ling back.

00:24:36.209 --> 00:24:37.570
I hope it's not too late.

00:24:51.530 --> 00:24:55.050
(Nie Jiuluo)

00:24:58.506 --> 00:24:59.385
Shen,

00:25:00.425 --> 00:25:03.705
could Earth Fiends actually be humans?

00:25:05.506 --> 00:25:06.145
What?

00:25:08.266 --> 00:25:15.826
Humans combined
with other species' genes became fiends.

00:25:16.625 --> 00:25:19.105
Lin Xirou has a method

00:25:19.105 --> 00:25:22.865
to reverse Yuwang Meat's effects

00:25:22.865 --> 00:25:24.986
and strip away the other genes.

00:25:25.266 --> 00:25:26.625
Are you saying

00:25:27.546 --> 00:25:29.385
they don't become human

00:25:30.945 --> 00:25:32.506
but revert to being human?

00:25:34.466 --> 00:25:37.066
I... I don't know.

00:25:38.945 --> 00:25:40.026
Wild guesses.

00:25:41.145 --> 00:25:41.945
Exactly.

00:25:42.546 --> 00:25:43.665
This explains

00:25:45.625 --> 00:25:47.586
how they came into being

00:25:48.826 --> 00:25:50.865
and how they became human.

00:25:51.506 --> 00:25:52.905
All of it makes sense now.

00:25:55.826 --> 00:25:57.145
If Yuwang Meat

00:25:57.945 --> 00:26:00.145
can enable both genetic fusion

00:26:01.546 --> 00:26:03.345
and reverse separation,

00:26:05.786 --> 00:26:07.306
then its applications

00:26:09.905 --> 00:26:11.226
would be endless.

00:26:13.425 --> 00:26:15.226
It can do good deeds

00:26:18.105 --> 00:26:20.826
and evil ones.

00:26:26.986 --> 00:26:28.145
Keep it safe first.

00:26:29.105 --> 00:26:29.945
Let's go check.

00:26:31.425 --> 00:26:32.226
Be good.

00:26:32.385 --> 00:26:34.665
Spend the New Year
with Grandma and Grandpa first.

00:26:34.865 --> 00:26:36.586
After the holidays when school starts,

00:26:36.786 --> 00:26:38.226
I will take you to school, okay?

