00:31:33.962 --> 00:31:37.203
I begged and pleaded with you before.

00:31:38.314 --> 00:31:39.994
Yet you insisted on leaving.

00:31:40.834 --> 00:31:43.115
And now you're exposing
your Mad Blade identity

00:31:43.994 --> 00:31:44.914
to return here,

00:31:46.155 --> 00:31:49.434
claiming to stand with us
against the enemy,

00:31:50.275 --> 00:31:51.715
but you're here to save him, right?

00:31:53.738 --> 00:31:55.858
The Hunters chose you to replace Jiang

00:31:56.658 --> 00:31:57.858
because they trusted you,

00:31:58.497 --> 00:31:59.937
